        "Description": "Orwell Newton, a Thai physicist. A recent lab report of his reveals a discovery that could change the way we consume vegetables. While this may sound good superficially, further investigation indicates that the discovery may negatively impact the poor population. His justifications did not convince our client.\r\rDaniel Alexander, his assistant. Her knowledge of the project may pose a threat even after his death. Our operatives have confirmed that she will mostly stay on the fourth floor.",
